Nigerian activist, Aisha Yesufu, and popular comedienne, Princess, have taken to social media to react after Nollywood actor, Olanrewaju James, better known as Baba Ijesha, was sentenced to 16 years imprisonment for sexually assaulting a 14-year-old minor.
