The actor was convicted by the Special Lagos Offences Court on a 4-count charge of sexual assault on a minor and sentenced to 16 years in jail but will spend five years in prison; he was lucky to have been left off the hook on 2 counts that could’ve earned him life!

Baba Ijesha was found guilty of indecent treatment and sexual assault of a minor between 2013-2014. The court finds that the prosecution successfully proved counts 2 and 4 of the charges.
